videos.description: John Fulkerson uses his strength to finish down low with a lefty layup to give Tennessee a 31-23 lead over No. 13 Oregon late in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fulkerson muscles inside for the layup) 2016/11/22

videos.headline: Fulkerson muscles inside for the layup

videos.description: Oregon's Jordan Bell grabs the loose ball and throws down the ferocious jam in the second half against Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Oregon's Bell throws the hammer down on Tennessee) 2016/11/22

videos.headline: Oregon's Bell throws the hammer down on Tennessee

videos.description: Oregon's Chris Boucher sends Tennessee's John Fulkerson's shot back twice with two big blocks late in the second half.
videos.headline: Oregon's Boucher stuffs Fulkerson twice

videos.description: Dillon Brooks hits a 3-pointer late in overtime to put Oregon up 68-65 on Tennessee, which would prove to be the game winner.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Brooks hits game-winning three for Oregon in OT) 2016/11/22

videos.headline: Brooks hits game-winning three for Oregon in OT

videos.description: In his second game back from injury, Dillon Brooks makes up for missing a shot at the buzzer in regulation with the dagger in overtime in No. 13 Oregon's 69-65 win over Tennessee.
videos.headline: Brooks' clutch shot gives Oregon OT win
